metadata.name: The Algorithm DAO
metadata.description:
The Algorithm DAO is a community for crypto & music enthusiasts.  
We operate under a shared goal, give each member equal say in making decisions, and give people a fair opportunity to own something of value they couldn't do on their own. 
Our DAO Buys Bitcoin, NFTS, Music Royalties via Sound Exchange, and Creates Music that generates additional streaming and publishing royalties for the DAO and the hodlers.

Investors are always looking for ways to protect their money while maximizing overall returns. Investing in NFTs, art, and Music royalties as a DAO gives our investors an opportunity to own assets that will generate Lump Sums & Residuals in the future.

Music Royalties provide a great option for long term residual earning. Owners of intellectual property get paid every time someone uses their work. They create an asset once, and then collect payment over and over again. So outside of our DAO doing investing, we'll be creating hundreds of songs that will generate additional revenue and earnings for The Algorithm DAO community. 

Check out some of the Algorithm Music: http://www.AlgorithmMusicMetaverse.io
